question.title: Jsoup Java get a specific td available-day
question.body:
I have the following code:

Document doc =
    Jsoup.connect("https://dgpci.mai.gov.ro/drpciv-booking/formular/35/vehicleFirstRegistration")
         .get();
Elements tds = doc.select("table.calendar-table tbody tr td.col-sm-1.available-day");
for (Element e : tds) {
    System.out.println(e.text());
}

I need to print the first day with classes: col-sm-1 and available-day.
